OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774793494
OL,3,CBenefit cheat who claimed anxiety left
OL,4,Cher housebound caught ziplining in
OL,5,CMexico
OL,7,FA woman who defrauded more than
OL,8,F#23,000 in benefits claiming she was
OL,9,Ftoo ill to go outside was caught
OL,10,Fsurfing and ziplining in Mexico.
OL,12,FCatherine Wieland, 33, claimed she
OL,13,Fsuffered anxiety so crippling she was
OL,14,Fhousebound, but the Department for
OL,15,FWork and Pensions (DWP) said it
OL,16,Fdiscovered she had been lying about
OL,17,Fher condition.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
