OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774793494
OL,3,CBenefit cheat who claimed anxiety left
OL,4,Cher housebound caught ziplining in
OL,5,CMexico
OL,7,FThe DWP said it found evidence of
OL,8,FWieland, from Goring-by-Sea, West
OL,9,FSussex, surfing in Cancun and visiting
OL,10,FThorpe Park three times, all while
OL,11,Fracking up tens of thousands of pounds
OL,12,Fin Personal Independence Payments
OL,13,F(Pip) over more than two years.
OL,15,FShe also spent money on manicures,
OL,16,Ftanning sessions and trips to a
OL,17,Fprivate Harley Street dentist.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774793494
OL,3,CBenefit cheat who claimed anxiety left
OL,4,Cher housebound caught ziplining in
OL,5,CMexico
OL,7,FWhen investigators confronted her with
OL,8,Fbank statements she told them: "I
OL,9,Fdidn't realise you're not allowed to
OL,10,Fleave your house", the DWP said.
OL,12,FWhile claiming her health was so poor
OL,13,Fshe could not cook or wash herself,
OL,14,FWieland made 76 beauty appointments,
OL,15,Fvisited 60 pubs, clubs and restaurants
OL,16,Fand spent money in foreign currencies.
OL,18,FAfter her luxury trip to Mexico,
OL,19,FWieland submitted a review claiming
OL,20,Fher condition had got worse.
OL,26,@pD@`OUrD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
