OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774793494
OL,3,CBenefit cheat who claimed anxiety left
OL,4,Cher housebound caught ziplining in
OL,5,CMexico
OL,7,FShe pleaded guilty to failing to
OL,8,Fnotify a change of circumstances and
OL,9,Fmust now repay the #23,662 stolen from
OL,10,Ftaxpayers between 2021 and 2024.
OL,12,FShe was sentenced on Thursday to 28
OL,13,Fweeks in custody, suspended for 18
OL,14,Fmonths, the DWP said.
OL,16,FAndrew Western, a minister in the DWP,
OL,17,Fsaid: "This is an insult to every
OL,18,Fhardworking taxpayer and to people who
OL,19,Fgenuinely depend on Pip.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
