OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774793494
OL,3,CBenefit cheat who claimed anxiety left
OL,4,Cher housebound caught ziplining in
OL,5,CMexico
OL,7,F"Wieland lied repeatedly, milked the
OL,8,Fsystem for every penny she could get
OL,9,Fand then had the nerve to claim her
OL,10,Fcondition was worsening while she was
OL,11,Fziplining and surfing in Mexico.
OL,13,F"We are committed to finding those who
OL,14,Ftry to defraud taxpayers, and they
OL,15,Fwill face the consequences."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUwD@\O]
